| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3746 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a700c137-8541-5b65-9bd9-1e28564196db"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
